a profile\n    96\t    Given the user sees a card for target user "Charlie"\n   
97\t    When the user swipes left or taps the pass button\n    98\t    Then a pa
ss action should be recorded in match_actions\n    99\t    And the target user s
hould be removed from the user\'s recommendation cache\n   100\t\n   101\t  Scen
ario: Duplicate swipe is idempotent\n   102\t    Given the user has already like
d target user "Bob"\n   103\t    When the user likes "Bob" again within 1 second
\n   104\t    Then the API should return success without creating a duplicate ma
tch_actions record\n   105\t    And no duplicate match should be created\n   106
\t\n   107\t  Scenario: User cannot swipe themselves\n   108\t    Given the user
sees their own profile in the candidate list by accident\n   109\t    When the u
ser tries to like themselves\n   110\t    Then the API should reject with code 1
000\n   111\t```\n   112\t\n   113\t#### 技术要求\n   114\t- 接口：`POST /matchi
ng/actions`（`target_id`, `action: \'like\' | \'pass\'`）。\n   115\t- 幂等性：`
match_actions` 表对 `(actor_id, target_id)` 建立唯一索引，重复插入被数据库拦截，
后端捕获异常返回成功。\n   116\t- 自身滑动校验：若 `target_id == actor_id`，返回
`code=1000`。\n   117\t- 滑动后清除 Redis 缓存 `recommendations:{user_id}`，确保
下次请求不再包含该用户。\n   118\t- `match_actions` 表字段：`id`, `actor_id`, `t
arget_id`, `action`（`like`/`pass`/`super_like`）, `created_at`。\n   119\t\n   
